        	<h2 style="width:100%; text-align:center; margin:0px; padding:0px;">Erik Mintz</h2>
            <h4 style="width:100%; text-align:center;">Founder & Chief Executive Officer DealCoachPro	</h4>
            <p>Mintz has 26 years of experience in the software development industry. He spent 8 years at Constant Contact as Director of EventSpot (2008 – 2015).  Prior to Constant Contact, Mintz was founder and CEO of e2M Systems which was acquired by Constant Contact in May, 2008. He started his career at IBM in Boca Raton, Florida working a total of 11 years in OS/2, Global Services and IBM Corporate. Mintz earned an MBA from MIT Sloan and Master of Engineering degree in Civil Engineering from Florida Atlantic University.</p>
