        	<h2 style="width:100%; text-align:center; margin:0px; padding:0px;">Bill Golder</h2>
            <h4 style="width:100%; text-align:center;">Founder at DealCoachPro</h4>
            <p>Golder has 24 years of executive experience in B2B sales and marketing. He is currently the founder and CEO of Slingshot Growth Partners, a Grand Rapids based consulting firm focused on helping small and mid-sized B2B companies improve sales effectiveness.  As Chief Sales Officer for Miller-Heiman, a premier sales training and consulting firm, Golder played a key role in helping the firm nearly double revenues over a 6-year period and achieve a private equity transaction in 2008. He earned his Bachelor’s degree from Western Michigan University and currently resides in Grand Rapids with his wife and two children.</p>
